	  	<p>GameINI is an on going project to simplify the modification of .ini files, specifically PC game settings files. The program allows a user to upload a file, then it utilizes Python's Config Parser tool to analyze and separate the different sections and settings included in the file. Django then takes this information to dynimically create a form based on that data. When the user is satisfied with their changes, the program creates a temporary file with the new data in the correct .ini format and hands that back to the user as a download. The original file uploaded is stored in an AWS RDS instance so that users can select a file that someone else has uploaded to edit to their own liking.</p>
